lead_paragraph: Challenger, 26, has performed at many sports events, soaring around the stadium and circling over the fans before landing on a handler’s left arm.

headline.main: Star of World Series, Final Four, Pro Bowls and Olympics? A Bald Eagle
headline.print_headline: Star of 5 World Series, a Final Four, 3 Pro Bowls and an Olympics? One Bald Eagle
